  "texts": [
    "In addition, in both experiments, location information is used.",
    "Experiments VI and VII remove the caption generation module based on Experiments I and II, respectively.",
    "The results show that the classification performance is significantly reduced, with the classification accuracy being 0.478 and 0.425, respectively.",
    "Finally, the influence of error propagation on model performance in DIC-Transformer is quantitatively analyzed.",
    "In effect, all the images in the dataset are used as the training set for the first stage disease region detection module."
